\c 46
\s Jakove anoenda kuEgipita
\p
\v 1 Zvino Israeri wakabva nezvose zvaaiva anazvo, ndokusvika kuBheeri-Shebha\x + 21.31,33; 26.23,33; 28.10.\x*, ndokubaira zvibairo kuna Mwari wababa vake Isaka\x + 26.24,25.\x*.
\v 2 Mwari ndokutaura kuna Israeri muzviratidzo\x + 15.1.\x* zveusiku, ndokuti: Jakove! Jakove! Iye ndokuti: Ndi\add ri\add* pano.
\v 3 Iye ndokuti: Ndiri Mwari, Mwari wababa vako\x + 28.13.\x*; usatya kuburukira kuEgipita; nokuti ndichakugadza kuva rudzi rukuru ikoko\x + 12.2. Det. 26.5.\x*;
\v 4 ini ndichaburukira newe kuEgipita, uye iniwo zvirokwazvo ndichakukwidza\add zve\add*\x + 15.16; 28.15; 48.21; 50.24. Eki. 3.8.\x*; uye Josefa achaisa ruoko rwake pameso ako\x + 50.1.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino Jakove wakasimuka kubva Bheeri-Shebha; vanakomana vaIsraeri ndokutakura Jakove baba vavo, nevanana vavo, nevakadzi vavo, mungoro Farao dzaaiva atumira kumutakura\x + 45.19,21,27.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino vakatora zvipfuwo zvavo nenhumbi dzavo dzavaiva vawana munyika yeKenani, ndokusvika kuEgipita, Jakove, nechizvarwa chake chose naye;
\v 7 vanakomana vake, nevana vevanakomana vake naye, vakunda vake, nevakunda vevanakomana vake, neicho chizvarwa chake chose, wakauya navo kuEgipita\x + 37.35. Josh. 24.4. Map. 105.23. Isa. 52.4.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Uye awa mazita evana vaIsraeri\x + Eki. 6.14-25. Eki. 1.1-5.\x* vakasvika kuEgipita: Jakove nevanakomana vake: Rubheni\x + Num.. 26.5-7. 1 Makor. 5.1-3.\x*, dangwe raJakove.
\v 9 Nevanakomana vaRubheni: Hanoki, naParu, naHezironi, naKarimi.
\p
\v 10 Nevanakomana vaSimioni: Jemueri, naJamini, naOhadhi, naJakini, naZohari, naShauri, mwanakomana wemukadzi muKenani.
\p
\v 11 Nevanakomana vaRevhi\x + 1 Makor. 6.1.\x*: Gerishoni, Kohati, naMerari.
\p
\v 12 Nevanakomana vaJudha\x + 1 Makor. 2.3; 4.21.\x*: Eri, naOnani, naShera, naPerezi, naZera; asi Eri naOnani vakafira munyika yeKenani\x + 1 Makor. 2.3; 4.21.\x*. Uye vanakomana vaPerezi vaiva Hezironi naHamuri\x + e 38.29. 1 Makor. 2.5.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Nevanakomana vaIsasikari\x + 1 Makor. 7.1.\x*: Tora, naPuvha, naJobho, naShimironi.
\p
\v 14 Nevanakomana vaZebhuruni: Seredhi, naEroni, naJahareeri.
\v 15 Ava vanakomana vaRea, vaakaberekera Jakove muPadhani-Aramu, nemukunda wake\x + 29.32-30.21.\x* Dhina; mweya yose yevanakomana vake nevakunda vake yaiva makumi matatu nemitatu.
\p
\v 16 Nevanakomana vaGadhi: Zifioni, naHagi, Shuni, naEzibhoni, Eri, naArodhi, naAreri\x + Num.. 26.15-17.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Nevanakomana vaAsheri\x + 1 Makor. 7.30.\x*: Jimina, naIshivha, naIshivhi, naBheria, naSera, hanzvadzi yavo; nevanakomana vaBheria: Hebheri, naMarikieri.
\v 18 Ava vanakomana vaZiripa\x + 30.10-13.\x*, Rabhani waakapa kuna Rea mukunda wake\x + 29.24.\x*, ndokuberekera ava Jakove: Mweya gumi nemitanhatu.
\p
\v 19 Vanakomana vaRakeri mukadzi waJakove: Josefa naBhenjamini.
\p
\v 20 Zvino kwakaberekerwa kuna Josefa munyika yeEgipita Manase naEfuremu, Asenati mukunda waPotifera mupristi weOni\x + 41.50.\x* vaakamuberekera.
\p
\v 21 Nevanakomana vaBhenjamini: Bhera, naBhekeri, naAshibheri, Gera, naNaamani, Ehi, naRoshi, Mupimi, naHupimi, naAridhi\x + Num.. 26.38-40. 1 Makor. 7.6-12; 8.1.\x*.
\v 22 Ava vanakomana vaRakeri, vakaberekerwa Jakove; mweya yose, gumi nemina.
\p
\v 23 Nevanakomana vaDhani: Hushimi.
\p
\v 24 Nevanakomana vaNafutari\x + 1 Makor. 7.13.\x*: Jazeeri, naGuni, naJezeri, naShiremi.
\v 25 Ava vanakomana vaBhiriha\x + 30.5-8.\x*, Rabhani vaakapa kuna Rakeri mukunda wake\x + 29.29.\x*, ndokuberekera Jakove ava; mweya yose minomwe.
\p
\v 26 Mweya yose yakasvika naJakove kuEgipita, ichibuda pachiuno chake, pasina vakadzi vevanakomana vaJakove, mweya yose makumi matanhatu nemitanhatu\x + Eki. 1.5. Det. 10.22. Mab. 7.14.\x*.
\v 27 Nevanakomana vaJosefa vaakaberekerwa muEgipita mweya miviri; mweya yose yeimba yaJakove yakauya muEgipita, makumi manomwe.
\p
\v 28 Zvino wakatuma Judha pamberi pake kuna Josefa kuti amurairire kuenda kuGosheni; zvino vakasvika munyika yeGosheni\x + 45.10.\x*.
\v 29 Josefa ndokusunga ngoro yake, ndokukwira kunosangana naIsraeri baba vake kuGosheni; ndokuzviratidza kwavari, ndokuwira pamutsipa wavo, ndokuchema pamutsipa wavo\x + 45.14.\x* nguva huru.
\v 30 Israeri ndokuti kuna Josefa: Ikozvino ngandife, zvandaona chiso chako, nokuti uchiri mupenyu.
\v 31 Zvino Josefa wakati kuvana vababa vake nekuimba yababa vake: Ndichakwira ndigozivisa Farao, uye nditi kwaari: Vana vababa vangu, neimba yababa vangu, vaiva vari munyika yeKenani vasvika kwandiri\x + 47.1.\x*;
\v 32 zvino varume vafudzi vemakwai, nokuti vaiva varume vezvipfuwo uye vaiva vauya nemakwai avo, nemombe dzavo, nezvose zvavaiva vanazvo.
\v 33 Zvino zvichaitika Farao paachakudanai agoti: Basa renyu chii\x + 47.3.\x*?
\v 34 Kuti muchati: Varanda venyu varume vekupfuwa\x + 46.32.\x* kubva paudiki hwedu kusvika ikozvino\x + 37.12.\x*, tese isu nemadzibaba edu; kuti mugare munyika yeGosheni, nokuti mufudzi umwe neumwe chinyangadzo kuVaEgipita\x + 43.32. Eki. 8.26.\x*.